OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with sunny spells.
OL,6,FScattered showers developing, clearing
OL,7,Flater in the afternoon. Temperatures
OL,8,Fcooler than yesterday in the west,
OL,9,Fsimilar in the east or perhaps a
OL,10,Flittle warmer near coasts, but still
OL,11,Fwarm or very warm overall.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny lingering showers easing,
OL,14,Fthen a dry night with clear spells.
OL,15,FOvernight temperatures rather fresher
OL,16,Fthan of late in northern parts,
OL,17,Fespecially in rural spots. Light winds.
OL,18,
OL,19,CSaturday:FDry with hazy sunshine and
OL,20,Fwarm or very warm for many again on
OL,21,FSaturday. Cooler near coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
